==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From [[πεντακίς]] {{GG|3999}} and [[χίλιοι]] {{GG|5507}}; 

===Pronunciation===
*πεντακισχίλιοι / pentakischilioi / pen-tak-is-khil'-ee-oy

===Cardinal number===
'''πεντακισχίλιοι'''

# five times a thousand: - five thousand.

